{"tid":1590090,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"如何正確召喚鶳神獸 以武制暴","createTime":"2019-09-23T14:28:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T14:45:54.000Z","uid":264872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"70247b62e6be56983988b60897e6b246077a0ff8","tid":1590090,"uid":264872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:28:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_2BEBdYJ68I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_2BEBdYJ68I&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obnyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=b45934c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_2BEBdYJ68I</a><br />\n「志森與志豪」最新一集：如何令獅島神戰打擊敵人 又唔會嚇壞自己人<br />\n<br />\n其中有幾個point 覺得講得幾有道理，我哋可以考慮改善：<br />\n<br />\n1. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文宣做足</span></span></strong>。自衛還擊嘅[red<span style=\"font-size: large;\">當刻</span>[/red] 已經要大大聲講返佢做過咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而不能夠單靠事後講解<br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>武力對等</strong></span></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果對方只係撕紙或者口角，仲要唔係現場斷正，或者我哋唔洗郁手先？如果對方手上有武器，我哋先制止佢？<br />\n正如我哋指責黑警濫捕 以及藍屍意圖謀殺僅僅係黐緊牆嘅手足，好大原因係因為武力嘅不對等&mdash;&mdash;我哋又係咪要變成好似佢哋咁樣嘅人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 美心可恥，但<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">食客同職員可能係同路人</span></span>，可能佢哋有做開義載，有捐錢捐物資甚至有一齊上前線，如果去圍/為難佢哋，會唔會嚇親佢哋？&mdash;&mdash;我相信佢哋未必會割，但係可能怕咗 從而唔敢再提出改善嘅建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&mdash;&mdash;我哋之所以能支撐著走到今日，正正係因為我哋從善如流，不斷改善不斷進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&mdash;&mdash;我哋要睇下做緊嘅嘢<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">係未對我哋嘅目標有幫助</span></strong>。<br />\n利申：絕對支持瘋狂撳紙仔瘋狂book枱瘋狂飲茶覇位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4. 擔心嘅情景：會唔會有臥底狗/藍屍煽動人群去做<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">真。過激</span></span>嘅行動？例如打砸金舖etc 因為佢哋「係藍色企業」&mdash;&mdash;甚至僅僅係被傳，未fc嘅。<br />\n對方陰濕無恥，甚至<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">出臥底真係搶掠</span></span></strong>，從而嫁禍我哋，污名化呢個活動<br />\n利申絕對相信前線嘅判斷力，只係提醒有機會發生咁樣嘅情景，我哋要小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>政治的工作不只是要令支持自己的人繼續支持自己，而更是要令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己，改變想法，認同自己的方向。<br />\n<br />\n如是者，假如我們希望社會能夠寬容地看待被論定為「暴動」的「暴徒」，理解這些無聲者的訴求，接納這些無權者的諫言，我想，我們必須警惕每一言一行，到底會更接近目標，還是距離更遠呢？<br />\n<br />\n當本應解決社會問題的人選擇冷待，反而熱衷於將香港的命運放上賭桌作政治豪賭，我們需要的，不是以自己寶貴的生命和他們對賭，而是在苦難中煉成堅毅與盼望。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 上前線嘅和理非<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n721 811 831 never forget never forgive <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de0a80cf5d646f1886da3d3c8aeba45a8ec0b30a","tid":1590090,"uid":264872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70247b62e6be56983988b60897e6b246077a0ff8","tid":1590090,"uid":264872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:28:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_2BEBdYJ68I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_2BEBdYJ68I&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obnyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=b45934c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_2BEBdYJ68I</a><br />\n「志森與志豪」最新一集：如何令獅島神戰打擊敵人 又唔會嚇壞自己人<br />\n<br />\n其中有幾個point 覺得講得幾有道理，我哋可以考慮改善：<br />\n<br />\n1. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文宣做足</span></span></strong>。自衛還擊嘅[red<span style=\"font-size: large;\">當刻</span>[/red] 已經要大大聲講返佢做過咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而不能夠單靠事後講解<br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font