own.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自膠 第一段已經寫錯字<br />\n<br />\n獅鳥神獸"},{"pid":"3282ebfff89d7e22518cf2c7ccb0c754a7ee8c6d","tid":1590090,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:29:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"f0032118cdce6d77a2c9dff053ddac420a8600a7","tid":1590090,"uid":264872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:30:00.000Z","msg":"P牌無得自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ebe5c3c97292bb89ead960ddd9c127b8fa36599","tid":1590090,"uid":264872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:30:47.000Z","msg":"P牌自己覆自己"},{"pid":"801e2b1e2f9c7698288d92ba07bc3a6b4402c361","tid":1590090,"uid":264872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:45:43.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dce436b13c6df3e130eef1296b49a31056986d6c","tid":1590090,"uid":264872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:45:54.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}